      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, honest classic with lots of vintage charm and a great opportunity to get into an enjoyable driver. This fair-condition car presents well enough to turn heads, but it does show visible age, cosmetic wear, and the small imperfections you\u2019d expect from an older vehicle that\u2019s been used and enjoyed. A solid choice for someone who wants a character-filled classic to drive, improve, and appreciate over time.",
