    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a practical budget option for someone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project. It shows its age, but it still offers dependable everyday utility, a straightforward ownership experience, and an accessible entry price that is hard to ignore. An excellent opportunity for a cost-conscious buyer who recognizes value where it counts.",
