    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great budget commuter, learner car, or project. It\u2019s priced fairly, reflects its condition, and could be a smart buy for someone handy or simply needing affordable transport. If you want something inexpensive without any sugar-coating, this is a straightforward deal.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with strong enthusiast potential. The drivetrain feels eager, the engine pulls cleanly, and the chassis has the kind of honest, analog character that\u2019s getting harder to find. Not a cosmetic queen and best approached as a driver/project, but it presents as a usable platform with good bones for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and straightforward maintenance. Great candidate for a budget commuter, weekend tinkering build, or parts runner with plenty of life left in it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
